      "span_text": "In the case of 5-D Gauss-Bonnet gravity with (positive or negative) cosmological term, λ = 1/4 (in Geometric units) has a critical value and the symmetry enhances to the full SO(4, 2) group and the 5-D Gauss-Bonnet gravity action with cosmological term is Chern-Simons Lagrangian for the AdS group [CITATION_2]"
